## 4. Player and Object Query API

### PlayerList (`/GameEngine/Include/Common/PlayerList.h`)

```cpp
extern PlayerList *ThePlayerList;

class PlayerList : public SubsystemInterface, public Snapshot {
    Int getPlayerCount();                           // total including neutral
    Player *getNthPlayer(Int i);                    // iterate by index 0..count-1
    Player *getNeutralPlayer();                     // always players[0]
    Player *getLocalPlayer();                       // the human player
    Player *findPlayerWithNameKey(NameKeyType key); // lookup by name
    Player *getPlayerFromMask(PlayerMaskType mask);
    void setLocalPlayer(Player *player);
};
```

### Player (`/GameEngine/Include/Common/Player.h`)

Key attributes accessible from `Player*`:
```cpp
UnicodeString getPlayerDisplayName();
AsciiString getSide();                    // "USA", "China", "GLA"
AsciiString getBaseSide();
PlayerIndex getPlayerIndex();             // 0-based integer
PlayerMaskType getPlayerMask();           // 1 << playerIndex
PlayerType getPlayerType();               // human vs AI
Money *getMoney();                        // current funds
Energy *getEnergy();                      // power state
Bool canBuild(const ThingTemplate *);
Bool canAffordBuild(const ThingTemplate *);
```

### Object (`/GameEngine/Include/GameLogic/Object.h`)

Object inherits from `Thing` which provides:
```cpp
const Coord3D *getPosition() const;           // world position (from Thing.h)
const ThingTemplate *getTemplate() const;     // unit type template
```

Direct Object accessors:
```cpp
ObjectID getID() const;
Object* getNextObject();                      // linked-list traversal
Team* getTeam();
Player* getControllingPlayer() const;
Relationship getRelationship(const Object *that) const;
Bool isDestroyed() const;
Bool isMobile() const;
Bool isAbleToAttack() const;
AIUpdateInterface *getAIUpdateInterface();
BodyModuleInterface *getBodyModule() const;   // health
VeterancyLevel getVeterancyLevel() const;
```

### Full object iteration pattern:
```cpp
for (Object *obj = TheGameLogic->getFirstObject(); obj; obj = obj->getNextObject()) {
    Player *owner = obj->getControllingPlayer();
    const Coord3D *pos = obj->getPosition();
    const ThingTemplate *tmpl = obj->getTemplate();
    // ...
}
```

